Description

The Tork SmartOne® dispenser for toilet paper in elevation design is a modern and efficient dispenser system for demanding washrooms with high visitor frequency. The individual towel removal can reduce consumption by up to 40% compared to conventional dispensers for jumbo toilet paper, so that more toilet visits are possible per roll. Tork Elevation dispensers are characterized by a modern, functional design that makes a good impression on guests.

• Robust design with locking mechanism to protect the reel and prevent theft in demanding environments

• Single sheet removal reduces consumption by up to 40%

• High capacity: less maintenance and less risk of paper bottlenecks

• Hygienic: You only touch the sheet that you are using

Sales unit: 1 dispenser
